{"tid":901303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Pence籲中國改變行為　避免與美國陷入新冷戰","createTime":"2018-11-14T01:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T05:10:04.000Z","uid":8543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4863a4d97815ba2f50259eac8b7e8a8169d32ffe","tid":901303,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"美國副總統Pence說，中國應該改變行為，避免與美國陷入新的冷戰。<br />\n<br />\nPence接受《華盛頓郵報》專訪時表示，總統Trump的態度是，美方希望確保中方知道美方的立場，以及美方準備怎樣做，以便北京能夠帶著具體的建議到阿根廷，解決美方面對的貿易赤字等問題。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，中國必須在知識產權盜竊，強制技術轉讓，限制進入中國市場，尊重國際規則和規範，以及限制國際水域航行自由等方面做出讓步。假如中方未能提出令到美方滿意的建議，美國準備在經濟、外交和政治方面，對中國增加施壓。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428178-20181114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428178-20181114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ixLiYFCu732OhaqVDeQPpDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=52f6e967\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428178-20181114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9f3db78b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428178-20181114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1dcf443198069d131e86a37993d339add2d59e40","tid":901303,"uid":42921,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"支國又可以準備假條約，同一國兩制一樣，西方仲未學精，好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22adf719df70ad3d506217720ca363e899faf30","tid":901303,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dcf443198069d131e86a37993d339add2d59e40","tid":901303,"uid":42921,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"支國又可以準備假條約，同一國兩制一樣，西方仲未學精，好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj